And so we're not going to be
able to get the job done.

00:04:45.970 --> 00:04:48.633
If we have a high level of
fitness, it means we're going

00:04:48.633 --> 00:04:51.490
to get the task done and return
and make everything

00:04:51.490 --> 00:04:52.590
successful.

00:04:52.590 --> 00:04:53.410
It's tough.

00:04:53.410 --> 00:04:56.346
It's not easy, but the
rewards are there.

